'''无机焦磷酸酶'''（{{lang-en|Inorganic Pyrophosphatase}}，简称为'''焦磷酸酶'''）是一种催化一分子[[焦磷酸盐|焦磷酸盐]]转化为两分子[[磷酸盐|磷酸盐]]离子的酶<ref name="pmid5342521">{{cite journal |author=Harold FM |title=Inorganic polyphosphates in biology: structure, metabolism, and function |journal=Bacteriol Rev |volume=30 |issue=4 |pages=772–94 |pmid=5342521 |pmc=441015 |doi= |url=|date=December 1966}}</ref>。这是一个高[[放能|放能]]的反应，因此此反应可偶联到一些热力学上不利的转化，以便驱动这些转化进行到完全<ref name="pmid11401820">{{cite journal |author=Terkeltaub RA |title=Inorganic pyrophosphate generation and disposition in pathophysiology |journal=Am. J. Physiol., Cell Physiol. |volume=281 |issue=1 |pages=C1–C11 |pmid=11401820 |doi= |url=|date=July 2001}}</ref>。此酶的功能乃是在[[脂代谢|脂代谢]]（包括脂合成与降解）、钙吸收以及骨形成<ref name="pmid4327778">{{cite journal |author=Orimo H, Ohata M, Fujita T |title=Role of inorganic pyrophosphatase in the mechanism of action of parathyroid hormone and calcitonin |journal=Endocrinology |volume=89 |issue=3 |pages=852–8 |pmid=4327778 |doi= 10.1210/endo-89-3-852|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_endocrinology_1971-09_89_3/page/852|date=September 1971}}</ref><ref name="pmid16181808">{{cite journal |author=Poole KE, Reeve J |title=Parathyroid hormone - a bone anabolic and catabolic agent |journal=Curr Opin Pharmacol |volume=5 |issue=6 |pages=612–7 |pmid=16181808 |doi=10.1016/j.coph.2005.07.004 |url=|date=December 2005}}</ref>和DNA合成<ref name="lehninger">{{Cite book | last = Nelson | first = David L. | coauthors = Cox, Michael M. | year = 2000 | title = Lehninger Principles of Biochemistry, 3rd ed. | publisher = Worth Publishers | location = New York | isbn = 1-57259-153-6 | pages = 937}}</ref>中扮演重要角色，其他[[生物化学|生物化学]]转化也是如此<ref name="pmid17981157">{{cite journal |author=Ko KM, Lee W, Yu JR, Ahnn J |title=PYP-1, inorganic pyrophosphatase, is required for larval development and intestinal function in C. elegans |journal=FEBS Lett. |volume=581 |issue=28 |pages=5445–53 |pmid=17981157 |doi=10.1016/j.febslet.2007.10.047 |url=|date=November 2007}}</ref><ref name="pmid20332330">{{cite journal |author=Usui Y, Uematsu T, Uchihashi T, ''et al.'' |title=Inorganic polyphosphate induces osteoblastic differentiation |journal=J. Dent. Res. |volume=89 |issue=5 |pages=504–9 |pmid=20332330 |doi=10.1177/0022034510363096 |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-dental-research_2010-05_89_5/page/504|date=May 2010}}</ref>。


